These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: orchid, lily
There 2 different types of food: cucumber, strawberry
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, taxi
1. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person who growslily is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Flower   | lily    | orchid |
| Food         | strawberry | cucumber    |
| Transport     | roller     | taxi      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, snowboarding
2 different pets are kept: hamster, turtle
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | sprite  | mirinda   |
| Sport   | snowboarding | parkour  |
| Pet     | turtle   | hamster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, writing
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, bus
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, july
1. the person who's hobby is writing is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | collecting   | writing  |
| Transport   | bus | airplane  |
| Birthday         | october   | july |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
