The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, volleyball
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, r&b
1. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Food          | pomegranate | raspberry |
| Sport   | volleyball   | tennis   |
| Music-Genre     | r&b       | electronic      |

