.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daisy, iris
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, dancer
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, train
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the accountant##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
3. the person who growsdaisy is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Flower    | iris | daisy     |
| Job     | dancer | accountant |
| Transport   | train | boat    |

