.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-11::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  chef, coach
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, swisher
2 different pets are kept: dog, turtle
1. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
2. the swisher-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the coach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Job           | coach     | chef |
| Cigar   | swisher | ritmeester  |
| Pet     | turtle      | dog |

