.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, rock-climbing
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, siglo
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: scientific, western
1. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | collecting |
| Cigar   | dannemann     | siglo     |
| Movie-Genre           | western          | scientific     |

