.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-20::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, july
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, techno
There 2 different types of food: artichoke, watermelon
1. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of techno is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Birthday   | march | july |
| Music-Genre   | disco  | techno  |
| Food     | watermelon | artichoke    |

 